    13	# Filter Today
    14	
    15	<!-- sk-doc-template: skill_asset_feature_catalog -->
    16	
    17	---
    18	
    19	## 1. OVERVIEW
    20	
    21	Server-side date filter returning tasks due between the current local midnight and the next local midnight, using the machine's local clock — not the workspace timezone.
    22	
    23	---
    24	
    25	## 2. HOW IT WORKS
    26	
    27	Combines with tag and team filters. Use `cupt list --today --json` as the standard agent daily-queue fetch.
