    13	# Offline Listing
    14	
    15	<!-- sk-doc-template: skill_asset_feature_catalog -->
    16	
    17	---
    18	
    19	## 1. OVERVIEW
    20	
    21	Returns task data from the local cache without making an API call. Requires prior caching via `cupt list` (auto-caches each run) or `cupt prefetch`.
    22	
    23	---
    24	
    25	## 2. HOW IT WORKS
    26	
    27	Useful in network-restricted environments or for fast repeated reads. Stale cache risk: data may be seconds to hours old depending on last API call.
    28	
    29	---
    30	
