    13	# Show Config
    14	
    15	<!-- sk-doc-template: skill_asset_feature_catalog -->
    16	
    17	---
    18	
    19	## 1. OVERVIEW
    20	
    21	Prints the current cupt configuration: Workspace ID, Default List ID, User ID, Authenticated state, and Auth Method (Personal API Token vs OAuth). Never prints any part of the token itself, masked or otherwise.
