    13	# Add Tag
    14	
    15	<!-- sk-doc-template: skill_asset_feature_catalog -->
    16	
    17	---
    18	
    19	## 1. OVERVIEW
    20	
    21	Adds a tag to the specified task. The tag must already exist in the workspace — cupt does not create new tags.
    22	
    23	---
    24	
    25	## 2. HOW IT WORKS
    26	
    27	Used in agent queue management: add tags like `needs_review`, `processed`, or `blocked` to signal state. Tag names are case-sensitive and must match exactly.
    28	
    29	---
    30	
