    13	# Status Schema by Task
    14	
    15	<!-- sk-doc-template: skill_asset_feature_catalog -->
    16	
    17	---
    18	
    19	## 1. OVERVIEW
    20	
    21	Queries the status schema for the list that contains the specified task. Returns all status names and their types. The closed status is marked explicitly.
    22	
    23	---
    24	
    25	## 2. HOW IT WORKS
    26	
    27	CRITICAL for agents: always call `cupt statuses <id>` before `cupt done <id>`. Status names vary per list — 'Done' in one list may be 'Complete', 'Shipped', or 'Closed' in another. Never hardcode status names.
    28	
