    13	
    14	# Spec Kit Memory: Feature Catalog
    15	
    16	This document is the current feature inventory for the Spec Kit Memory system. It describes live MCP tools, pipeline stages, verification surfaces, and the supporting workflow scripts that ship with the same skill package.
    17	
    18	---
    19	
    20	## 1. OVERVIEW
    21	
    22	Use this catalog as the canonical inventory for both current behavior and delivered refinements. The numbered sections below group the live system by feature area so operators can move from the top-level reference into the per-feature files without losing implementation, validation, or rollout context.
    23	
